299
00:19:46,600 --> 00:19:48,400
I won't leave.

300
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,800
Then have lunch with me after the interview.

301
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:55,500
I heard from Jia Shi Li there's a very good...

