00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:58,200
Can you not think about food right now?

303
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,500
Go now.

304
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:04,000
Eat with me.

305
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,400
Come back.

306
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:21,900
There, go ahead.

307
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,500
Don't leave.

308
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,800
Get ready. He's coming.

309
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,200
Come on.

310
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:41,600
