- Hello.

311
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,800
Come on. Here.

312
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:44,400
Please take a seat.

313
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:47,100
- Please.
- Sit here.

314
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:50,000
You look great in this suit.

315
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,400
Thank you.

316
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,500
We'll start when you're ready.

317
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:00,000
We can start anytime.

318
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,400
Okay.

319
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:04,600
Take this first.

320
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:05,600
This is my business card.

321
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:07,400
I didn't get to give it to you last time.

322
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,000
Thank you.

323
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:14,200
I think I was in good condition.
