00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:18,700
Sorry. The athlete needs to rest.

327
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:21,700
When did you start doing sports?

328
00:21:21,700 --> 00:21:25,200
When I was seven or eight years old.

329
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,900
What do your parents do for a living?

330
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:30,400
My parents run a small business.

331
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:32,800
That is to say that your family doesn't know much

332
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:34,500
