472
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,400
Then get out of here!

473
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,400
Don't stay here!

474
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,200
Fine.

475
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:37,200
I see through you now.

476
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:39,500
You want to get rid of me after using me, right?

477
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:41,800
Burning the bridge you've crossed.

478
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,300
Fine.

479
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,400
- Don't.
- Get out!

480
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:48,000
Don't.

481
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:51,000
I'll talk to him. You go out first.

482
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,700
Be quiet.

483
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,800
Come on, tell me.

484
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:01,600
Why don't you want to go?

485
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:06,300
It's all due to him.

486
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,600
He is sick and tired of me.

487
00:28:08,600 --> 00:28:10,400
Now he can send me away.

488
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,800
Are you angry he refused

489
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:14,800
