491
00:28:16,800 --> 00:28:19,100
Why doesn't he want to accompany me there?

492
00:28:19,100 --> 00:28:20,800
He must be so tired of me

493
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:22,000
and is taking this opportunity

494
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:24,200
to get rid of me outright.

495
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:30,600
It's not that Coach Wu

496
00:28:30,600 --> 00:28:32,800
