506
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:57,800
He knows his limits and has to stop here.

507
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:58,800
Letting you go alone

508
00:28:58,800 --> 00:29:00,900
will get you assigned to a better coach

509
00:29:00,900 --> 00:29:03,600
and have more chances to compete.

510
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:07,400
So this is what he thinks.

511
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:09,200
Is he stupid?

512
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:11,000
You...

513
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,800
You should just believe Coach Luo.

514
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:14,400
They grew up together.

515
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:17,200
She knows Coach Wu the best.

516
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,600
He still didn't have to do all this.

517
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:24,600
Why does he think he isn't capable?

518
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:26,600
I want him.

519
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,800
I want only him.

520
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:35,100
Don't act like a child, okay?

521
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:36,600
If you really miss him,

522
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:40,000
then train hard and get great results.

523
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:42,000
What's so hard about getting results?

524
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:44,800
I just don't want to go alone.

525
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:48,800
Don't you still have him?

526
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:51,200
We said you two must depend on each other.

527
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:53,600
Let's get started now.

528
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:54,400
It's mealtime.

529
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:56,100
Just go eat together.

530
00:29:56,100 --> 00:29:57,900
No.

531
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:03,400
Come on.

532
00:30:07,800 --> 00:30:09,000
I'm hungry.

533
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:11,600
Let's go for some good food.

534
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:15,200
Once we join the national team, we can only eat at the cafeteria.

535
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:17,200
Eat well.

536
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,000
You're buying.

537
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:49,800
Don't worry too much.

538
00:30:49,800 --> 00:30:52,400
On the national team, just work hard.

539
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:54,000
It's okay if you don't do well.

540
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:57,700
Coach Wu and I will always support you.

541
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:02,700
But can I ask you for a favor?

542
00:31:02,700 --> 00:31:04,600
Go ahead.

543
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:06,600
Give him another chance.

544
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:19,800
Say something.

545
00:31:30,100 --> 00:31:33,100
Train hard once you get there,

546
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:36,000
