549
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,400
One thing:

550
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:45,000
don't get injured.

551
00:31:47,800 --> 00:31:50,100
How can you just rain on our parade?

552
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,000
We haven't even gone yet.

553
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:53,400
Why can't we achieve anything great?

554
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:55,200
He's not good at sports.

555
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:57,000
You're not a good enough person.

556
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,600
Well...

557
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:13,000
Coach Wu meant

558
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:14,800
that after you go there,

559
00:32:14,800 --> 00:32:17,700
you must take care of yourselves.

560
00:32:17,700 --> 00:32:19,600
Don't be too stressed.

561
00:32:23,500 --> 00:32:24,600
Right.

562
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:27,800
Just don't be stressed out.

563
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:30,800
